    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\n```\n# nvim1\nnvim --clean --listen /tmp/test\n# nvim2\nnvim --clean --server /tmp/test --headless -c \"echo serverlist()\"\n```\n\nnvim2 does not actually connect to the `--server`, nor does it report an error.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nNvim should either report an error saying that `--server` isn't supported with `--headless`, or actually connect to the server and DWIM.",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
